Titolo: Destroy All Humans! 2

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Destroy All Humans! 2 is an action-adventure video game developed by Pandemic Studios and published by THQ for PlayStation 2 and Xbox. It is the sequel to Destroy All Humans! and the second installment in the Destroy All Humans! franchise. It also marks the last game in the series to be developed by Pandemic Studios, as the company was later acquired by Electronic Arts in 2007. A remake was announced by THQ Nordic in 2021.